    premiumIntroEn: "Tenerife is more than poolside and piña coladas — but you have to actively step out of the resort. The Teide, the Anaga mountains and La Laguna are genuine nature experiences on an island most people only know as a sun deck.",
    mustSeeDe: ["Teide-Nationalpark früh morgens", "La Laguna Altstadt (UNESCO)", "Masca-Schlucht für Wanderer"],
    mustSeeEn: ["Teide National Park early in the morning", "La Laguna old town (UNESCO)", "Masca gorge for hikers"],
